    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.4-5_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">4</fw>
                
                <fw type="imprint">
                    <hi rend="caps">TELEPHONE 1161
                
                    UNITED STATES
                
                    MANUFACTURING CORPORATION</hi> <hi rend="italics">Pratt, Kansas</hi>
                
                    <figure>
                        <figDesc>Shield</figDesc>
                        <p>THE US LINE</p>
                    </figure>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline><hi rend="underline">4-7-58</hi></dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt&#8212;</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>A friend of mine &#8212; Tom <hi rend="caps">R.</hi> Taylor &#8212; forwarded the newspaper clipping on your wifes auto accident on 4-3.</p>
                
                <p>I sincerely hope that your wife is fully recovered + that the police saw fit to treat you with the respect you deserve.</p>
                
                <p>You offer many fond memories of <hi rend="caps">M.U.</hi> &#8212; and I <hi rend="underline">thoroughly</hi> enjoyed my hours in your classes + above all else at school &#8212; my short visits in your office + at your home &#8212;</p>
                
                <p>I sincerely hope my son will have the opportunity of the friendship + guidence during his college days that I enjoyed with you.</p>
                
                <p>I have read + re-read your Cycle of
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="italics">Incorporated 1887</hi>
                    <hi rend="caps">WORLD'S LARGEST MANUFACTURER OF FLY SWATTERS AND CORN POPPERS</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.4-5_0002"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">5</fw>
                
                <fw type="imprint">
                    <hi rend="caps">TELEPHONE 1161
                
                    UNITED STATES
                
                    MANUFACTURING CORPORATION</hi> <hi rend="italics">Pratt, Kansas</hi>
                
                    <figure>
                        <figDesc>Shield</figDesc>
                        <p>THE US LINE</p>
                    </figure>
                </fw>
                
                    the West + gain something new out of it each time.</p>
                
                <p>Words cannot express my devotion to you + how often I think of our conversations.</p>
                
                <p>My sincere regards to you + Mrs. Neihardt + hopes that the future years are full of rewards + happiness and <hi rend="caps">NO MORE</hi> accidents &#8212;</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Respectfully + Sincerely</salute>
                
                Bud
                BB Shafter
                </closer>
                
                <postscript>
                    <opener><hi rend="caps">P.S.</hi></opener> <p>Please offer my regards to Dean English when you see him &#8212;</p>
                </postscript>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="italics">Incorporated 1887</hi>
                    <hi rend="caps">WORLD'S LARGEST MANUFACTURER OF FLY SWATTERS AND CORN POPPERS</hi>
                </fw>
                
            </div1>
